    <h2>Help</h2>

    <h3>Accessing Books</h3>
    <p>There are several ways to find and read books in the collection:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Browse by Subject</strong> &mdash; explore titles organized by academic discipline.</li>
      <li><strong>Browse by Title</strong> &mdash; browse alphabetically through all titles in the collection.</li>
      <li><strong>UC affiliates</strong> &mdash; faculty, staff, and students at any University of California
        campus have free access to the full collection when connected to the UC network or via VPN.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Getting Help</h3>
    <p>
      If you have questions about accessing a title, trouble loading a page, or general inquiries about
      the collection, please contact the California Digital Library:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Visit the <a href="https://cdlib.org">California Digital Library website</a></li>
      <li>Email <a href="mailto:cdl@www.cdlib.org">cdl@www.cdlib.org</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
